item.title: "Salvation by Promise, Not Performance"
item.description:
Most of us have the desire to do well in the jobs and opportunities before us. If you're an athlete or gamer, the bottom line is that you want to win. In this week's Harvest Valor Podcast, Pastor KC shares how our salvation is not something we need to compete for to win or keep.Â  We can live in light of God's already-given promise to us.
